{
  "2363160": {
    "name": "Haphazard Angel",
    "steam_appid": 2363160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/3efec1391afbb85683219204b4385306.poster.avif?t=1760603976\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/3efec1391afbb85683219204b4385306.webm?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到《冒失天使》！和“损友”一起体验“友尽”的乐趣！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，我是卡兹菲尔·巴尔提乌尔·塔布里斯，简称卡兹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到这款“损人利己”的游戏！在《冒失天使》中，2-4名玩家将共同操控一个华丽又笨拙的天使。你将控制它的四只翅膀之一，团队合作至关重要……直到你不想合作的时候！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/90bfe78b859c84b0b3906f9fff4337b2.poster.avif?t=1760603976\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/90bfe78b859c84b0b3906f9fff4337b2.webm?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/90bfe78b859c84b0b3906f9fff4337b2.mp4?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >分担“重负”，共享“混乱”！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2-4名玩家</strong> - 叫上你的“猪队友”，拿起手柄！你们需要（有时是假装需要）合作来完成目标！聚会和游戏之夜的绝佳选择！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一只天使，四只翅膀</strong> - 每位玩家控制一只翅膀，但你们共享同一个身体。我们的身体！沟通是关键——祝你们好运！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>七宗罪</strong> - 选择一双灵感来源于七宗罪的翅膀。每种翅膀都有其独特的优势和劣势——有些互补，有些冲突。你们能好好相处吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/6b4584548555ab8e3b536030fc551fdf.poster.avif?t=1760603976\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/6b4584548555ab8e3b536030fc551fdf.webm?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/6b4584548555ab8e3b536030fc551fdf.mp4?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【剧情模式】通往天堂的阶梯，亦或坠入地狱的坦途，你的命运由你选择！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你失去了恩典，被贬入炼狱。现在，你面临着一个重大的抉择：攀登 10000 米充满险阻的天堂阶梯，以重获你的地位；或者沿着 10000 米危机四伏的地狱之路向下探索……寻找某些别的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从幽暗的深渊开始你的旅程，坚定你的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/1017212d03e546bc36f35528e6161c01.poster.avif?t=1760603976\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/1017212d03e546bc36f35528e6161c01.webm?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/1017212d03e546bc36f35528e6161c01.mp4?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【街机模式】多种获胜方式，等你来发现！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作是基础</strong> - 仅凭一只翅膀，卡兹寸步难行。收集圣环能帮助卡兹重返天堂！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞争是必然</strong> - 只有一只翅膀能够拾取圣环和邪恶精华。拾取的越多，玩家对卡兹菲尔的影响力就越大。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/64843ff878b77d05762b086b1b6e1d34.poster.avif?t=1760603976\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/64843ff878b77d05762b086b1b6e1d34.webm?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363160/extras/64843ff878b77d05762b086b1b6e1d34.mp4?t=1760603976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作简单易学：挥动翅膀，在混乱中摸索前进，与你的队友合作（或互相使绊）！无论你们是在同一屋檐下进行本地合作，还是在线组队，《冒失天使》都能带来欢乐与抓狂并存的完美体验！</p>",
